# Cloudflare Pages Redirects
# Redirect www to apex domain (only after DNS configured in Cloudflare)

# NOTE: These redirects only apply when:
# 1. Domain is connected to Cloudflare Pages project
# 2. DNS records are configured:
#    - incany.be A/AAAA records pointing to Cloudflare Pages
#    - www.incany.be CNAME pointing to incany.be
# 3. Custom domain is verified in Cloudflare Pages dashboard

# Redirect www to non-www (apex domain)
https://www.incany.be/* https://incany.be/:splat 301!

# This redirect will NOT cause issues with preview deployments
# because preview URLs (*.pages.dev) don't match the www.incany.be pattern
